# AI Streaming (Diagnosis Advice)

Prefer **Vercel AI SDK** (`ai`, `@ai-sdk/openai`, `@ai-sdk/anthropic`) for new advice routes.

## Structured output
- Enforce JSON: `personalizedAdvice`, `dailyTip`, `affirmation`.
- Validate with Zod after stream completes; never trust raw model text blindly.
- System prompt + `AIPromptBlueprint.responseSchema` must stay in sync.

## Providers
- OpenAI / Anthropic via AI SDK when keys exist.
- Groq fallback is acceptable for dev; keep behavior identical at the type layer.

## Client
- Stream to UI character-by-character when possible; show `AdviceSkeleton` until parsed.
- Abort in-flight streams on unmount (`AbortController`).
- Never merge advice stream state into diagnosis engine hook.
